# Steps to install SASS
1. Installed NVM to manage Node versions:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed and reopened the terminal

3. Installed Node.js v20.16:
   nvm install 20.16.0

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4